---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="關於與聯繫" description="嗨，我是 Long —— 擁有 10 年經驗的 AI 與軟體資深從業者，常駐香港，服務全球客戶。" hideHeader={true}>
  
  <header class="mb-12 mt-8 fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-headline font-extrabold text-on-surface tracking-tight mb-6">
          關於與聯繫
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          嗨，我是 <strong>Long</strong> —— 擁有 10 年經驗的 AI 與軟體資深從業者，常駐香港，服務全球客戶。
      </p>
  </header>

  <div class="mb-12 mt-8">
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-lg">
          朋友和同事一直在問我同一個問題：<em>「為什麼 AI 沒有按照我要求的去做？」</em>在數據分析、汽車軟體、電腦視覺和醫療 AI 領域構建了 10 年產品後，我意識到差距不在於智慧 —— 而在於直覺。所以我構建了這個課程，旨在為人們提供與 AI 協作所需的心智模型，而不僅僅是學會使用它。
      </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Equation Banner Tagline -->
  <div class="flex justify-center mb-16 mt-8">
      <div class="equation-banner px-10 py-6 rounded-full inline-flex items-center gap-4 rotate-[-1deg] bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary text-white shadow-lg">
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold font-headline text-center text-white">我能為您提供關於 AI 的全方位協助</span>
      </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What I Do -->
  <div class="space-y-6 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">我的服務</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">🧭</span> AI 戰略與諮詢
              </h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">協助您的公司釐清在 AI 領域「應該做」和「不應該做」的事情。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">🛠️</span> 實施與開發
              </h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">不僅提供建議，還能親手構建。從原型開發到投入生產。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">🎓</span> 企業培訓
              </h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">從高管簡報到團隊實戰工作坊，為您量身定制合適水平的課程。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">⚙️</span> 流程自動化
              </h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">識別可自動化的環節，設計架構方案，並最終交付產品。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10 md:col-span-2">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">🔍</span> 技術盡職調查
              </h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">在您做出承諾前，評估 AI 供應商、審查架構並評估可行性。</p>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="bg-secondary-container rounded-xl p-8 flex gap-6 items-start mt-12">
      <span class="text-4xl leading-none hidden md:block">📧</span>
      <div class="space-y-4">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-on-secondary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">聯絡我</h4>
          <p class="text-on-secondary-container font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed">
              無論您是 5 人的新創公司還是 500 人的大企業，同樣的基本原理都適用，只是規模不同。讓我們聊聊吧。
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-on-secondary-container mt-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">person</span>
                  <span><strong>Long</strong> — 10 年 AI、數據與軟體經驗 · 加州大學柏克萊分校應用數學系</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">location_on</span>
                  <span>香港 · 服務全球客戶</span>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-6">
              <a href="mailto:longhui@berkeley.edu" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:underline text-lg">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">mail</span>
                  longhui@berkeley.edu
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/longhui1996" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:underline text-lg">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">link</span>
                  LinkedIn
              </a>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I Built This link -->
  <div class="mt-12 mb-16">
      <a href="/zh-hant-hk/special-how-i-built-this-01" class="group bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center gap-4 hover:bg-surface-container hover:shadow-md transition-all no-underline">
          <span class="text-3xl hidden md:block">🏗️</span>
          <div>
              <p class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface group-hover:text-accent transition-colors m-0">想看看我是如何構建這個網站的嗎？</p>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1 m-0">閱讀我是如何構建這整個課程的 —— 從大綱設計到 AI 輔助開發。</p>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary ml-auto group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
